title: Log in and file your Stamp Duty Land Tax return

heading_context: Log in and file your Stamp Duty Land Tax return
chunks.html_content: Log in to the HM Revenue and Customs (HMRC) Stamp Taxes Online service to file your Stamp Duty Land Tax (SDLT) return as a solicitor, agent or legal conveyancer.
chunks.plain_content:
Log in and file your Stamp Duty Land Tax return
Log in to the HM Revenue and Customs (HMRC) Stamp Taxes Online service to file your Stamp Duty Land Tax (SDLT) return as a solicitor, agent or legal conveyancer.

heading_context: Log in and file your Stamp Duty Land Tax return
chunks.html_content: If you’re filing a return for an additional residential property, choose code 04 when you pick a property type.
chunks.plain_content:
Log in and file your Stamp Duty Land Tax return
If you’re filing a return for an additional residential property, choose code 04 when you pick a property type.

heading_context: Log in and file your Stamp Duty Land Tax return
chunks.html_content: You need to register for Stamp Taxes Online before you can file your SDLT returns online.
chunks.plain_content:
Log in and file your Stamp Duty Land Tax return
You need to register for Stamp Taxes Online before you can file your SDLT returns online.

heading_context: Log in and file your Stamp Duty Land Tax return
chunks.html_content: You cannot use the online service if you’re an individual buying property and you aren’t represented by a solicitor, agent or legal conveyancer. Complete a paper return instead.
chunks.plain_content:
Log in and file your Stamp Duty Land Tax return
You cannot use the online service if you’re an individual buying property and you aren’t represented by a solicitor, agent or legal conveyancer. Complete a paper return instead.
